snippet.title: ELDERBORN Console Reveal Trailer (PS5, Xbox X|S)
snippet.description:
ELDERBORN - The Metal Action Fantasy Slasher with brutal FPP souls-like melee combat is coming to Xbox series X|S and Playstation 5.

Get ready to flex your barbaric muscles, crush skulls and hear your foes lamentation as you kick them off a cliff on the 8th of November 2024.

Wishlist on Playstation - https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011340
Wishlist on Xbox -  https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/elderborn/9p432dplr8tc

Early Preview keys for Influencers and Press:  https://www.lurkit.com/campaigns/elderborn
